teacheasy.xml

Enum XMLElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<XMLElement>
      • teacheasy.xml.XMLElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<XMLElement>

    public enum XMLElement
extends java.lang.Enum<XMLElement>
    This enumerated type contains an entry for any element the parser anticipates finding within an xml file. This allows for the 'string switching' method seen in the XMLParser class.
    Version:
    1.0 13 Feb 2015
    Author:
    Alistair Jewers
